  "title": "Electronics Operators x 50 @ AMK | Up to $12/hr & $10k in 3 months | Aircon Environment",
  "description": "<p><strong>Electronics Operators x 50 @ AMK | Up to $12/hr & $10k in 3 months | Aircon Environment</strong></p><p>📍 Location: Ang Mo Kio</p><p>📆 Work Days: 6 days, Monday – Saturday</p><p>💰 Hourly Pay: Up to $12/hour</p><ul><li>Morning Shift: $11/hr (7AM–3PM)</li><li>Noon Shift: $11/hr (3PM–11PM)</li><li>Night Shift: $12/hr (11PM–7AM)</li></ul><p><strong>🔧 Job Scope</strong></p><ul><li>Perform assembly and production duties</li><li>Wire insertion into plastic tubing</li><li>Conduct quality checks, picking, and packing tasks</li><li>Maintain cleanliness and follow safety procedures</li></ul><p><strong>🌟 Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Good eyesight and attention to detail</li><li>Min 3 months’ availability (convertible to permanent)</li><li>Preferably with prior operator or manufacturing experience</li><li>Comfortable working in air-conditioned, controlled environments (smock & hairnet required)</li></ul><p><strong>📩 Interested? Apply Now!</strong></p><p>Send your resume in MS Word format to: <a href=\"mailto:Vanessa.chua@crew.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Vanessa.chua@crew.sg</a></p><p>Please include your availability, notice period, and\nexpected salary.</p><p><em>* Only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</em></p><p>Vanessa Chua Peng Teng (R25158315)</p><p>HRnet Ventures Pte Ltd - CREW by HRnet</p><p>E.A. 24C2435</p>",
